#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/mounting.rst:2
msgid "本体检测（Mounting）"
msgstr "Body Inspection (Mounting)"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/mounting.rst:4
msgid "**此页面的用途**"
msgstr "**What this page covers**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/mounting.rst:6
msgid "检测元件本体的贴装缺陷，包括缺件、错件、损件、偏移、旋转与极性等。ROI 应覆盖元器件主体表面。"
msgstr ""
"Detects mounting defects on the component body — missing, wrong, damaged, "
"shifted, rotated, or reverse-polarity components. The ROI should cover the "
"body surface of the part."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/mounting.rst:8
msgid "**如何进入**"
msgstr "**How to open it**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/mounting.rst:10
msgid "模板编辑器中绘制对应 ROI 后，在参数面板中配置该工具的参数。"
msgstr ""
"Draw the corresponding ROI in the Template Editor, then configure the tool's"
" parameters in the parameter panel."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/mounting.rst:12
msgid "**操作流程**"
msgstr "**Workflow**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/mounting.rst
msgid "本体检测ROI示例"
msgstr "Example of a Body inspection ROI"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/mounting.rst:18
msgid "**位置与姿态**"
msgstr "**Position and pose**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/mounting.rst:20
msgid "**旋转角度 (°)（Max Rotation Angle）**：元件本体相对标准姿态的角度偏差；当偏差超过该阈值时判定为 NG。"
msgstr ""
"**Max Rotation Angle (°)**: angular deviation of the component body from the"
" golden pose; flagged NG when the deviation exceeds this threshold."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/mounting.rst:21
msgid "**X 偏移 (mm)（Shift X）/ Y 偏移 (mm)（Shift Y）**：样本元件与标准元件本体的平移偏差；超过阈值判 NG。"
msgstr ""
"**Shift X (mm) / Shift Y (mm)**: translational deviation of the inspected "
"body from the golden body; flagged NG when the shift exceeds the threshold."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/mounting.rst:23
msgid "**缺陷检测（AI）**"
msgstr "**Defect detection (AI)**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/mounting.rst:25
msgid ""
"**常规检测（Significant Defect Check）**：对元件本体的明显缺陷（缺件、错件、方向严重错误等）进行 AI 异常分数判定。"
msgstr ""
"**Significant Defect Check**: AI anomaly-score check for obvious body "
"defects — missing, wrong, or severely misoriented components."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/mounting.rst
msgid "本体AI分数分布示例"
msgstr "Example AI score distribution for body inspection"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/mounting.rst
msgid "本体AI分数分布示例2"
msgstr "AI score distribution — example 2"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/mounting.rst:35
msgid ""
"**损件检测（Subtle Defect Check）**：针对本体的破损、缺口等细微异常；检测前先将元件图像与标准样本自动对齐，再以 AI "
"异常分数判定，避免位置偏移导致误判。"
msgstr ""
"**Subtle Defect Check**: targets fine-grained body anomalies such as chips, "
"cracks, and damage. The image is first aligned to the golden sample before "
"the AI anomaly-score check, so positional drift doesn't trigger false "
"positives."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/mounting.rst
msgid "损件检测"
msgstr "Damaged-component inspection"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/mounting.rst
msgid "本体对齐后检测"
msgstr "Body inspection after alignment"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/mounting.rst
msgid "本体对齐后检测2"
msgstr "Body inspection after alignment — example 2"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/mounting.rst:49
msgid "**缺件检测（Missing Check）**：判定该位置是否缺少元件。"
msgstr ""
"**Missing Check**: decides whether the component is missing at this "
"location."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/mounting.rst:50
msgid ""
"**增强缺件检测（Enhanced Missing Check）**：利用对位结果在元件疑似缺失时提前告警；属实验性功能，当对位误判导致误报时可关闭。"
msgstr ""
"**Enhanced Missing Check**: uses the alignment result to fire an earlier "
"missing-component alert when the part appears absent. Experimental — disable"
" it if alignment misfires cause false positives."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/mounting.rst:52
msgid "**极性检测（AI，对齐后）**"
msgstr "**Polarity check (AI, after alignment)**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/mounting.rst:54
msgid ""
"**极性检测（Polarity Check）**：判断元件极性方向是否正确。检测前先对齐，并在 **极性 ROI** "
"区域内学习与判定极性特征，以识别极性反转。判定方式同样基于 AI 异常分数。"
msgstr ""
"**Polarity Check**: verifies that the component is mounted in the correct "
"polarity. The inspected image is aligned first, then the polarity feature is"
" learned and evaluated inside the **Polarity ROI** to catch reverse "
"polarity. The decision is also driven by the AI anomaly score."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/mounting.rst:55
msgid "**极性检测灵敏度（Polarity Sensitivity）**：调节极性判定的灵敏度；灵敏度越高越容易报出极性异常。"
msgstr ""
"**Polarity Sensitivity**: controls how aggressively polarity is flagged. "
"Higher sensitivity surfaces more polarity NGs."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/mounting.rst:56
msgid ""
"**极性 ROI（Polarity ROI）**：点击 *设置 ROI* 或在显示窗口中直接拖拽，框选用于极性判定的局部区域（通常为极性标识所在处）。"
msgstr ""
"**Polarity ROI**: click *Set ROI* or drag directly on the canvas to draw the"
" local region used for polarity evaluation — typically the area containing "
"the polarity marking."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/mounting.rst
msgid "极性检测框"
msgstr "Polarity inspection ROI"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/mounting.rst
msgid "极性检测"
msgstr "Polarity inspection"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/mounting.rst
msgid "极性检测2"
msgstr "Polarity inspection — example 2"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/mounting.rst:70
msgid "**其它**"
msgstr "**Other**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/mounting.rst:72
msgid "**启用遮罩（Enable Mask）**：对含有不固定字符 / 图案的区域进行遮蔽，避免其影响 AI 检测。"
msgstr ""
"**Enable Mask**: masks out areas that contain variable characters or "
"patterns so they don't disturb the AI decision."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/mounting.rst
msgid "遮罩"
msgstr "Mask"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/mounting.rst:79
msgid "**常见问题与提示**"
msgstr "**Common questions and tips**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/mounting.rst:83
msgid "**LED 灯极性识别不出**：手动开启 **极性检测** 子项；如频繁失败，可联系下一次模型迭代时强化 LED 极性样本。"
msgstr ""
"**LED polarity can't be recognized**: enable the **Polarity Check** sub-item"
" manually. If it fails repeatedly, request additional LED polarity samples "
"in the next model iteration."
